  "3184990": {
    "name": "诡秘推理",
    "steam_appid": 3184990,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《诡秘推理》</strong>是由BC工作室开发的一款主打高自由度的侦探玩法的新本格推理游戏。以“人与神共存的诡秘世界”为舞台，营造出理性与超自然交织的独特氛围。在使用经典的出示证物、寻找矛盾的方式解决案件之外，还可通过多种攻略途径抓获真凶，推理过程有更高自由度，并伴随丰富的彩蛋与随机事件。   </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>新本格推理</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《诡秘推理》融合超自然的奇幻设定与本格案件，拓展推理游戏可能性，将解谜的乐趣推向NEXT LEVEL!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏设定在一个虚构的“轻克苏鲁”世界——人与神共存的诡秘世界。这里有秘密组织<strong>AIB（异常事务调查局）</strong>潜藏于暗影中，细心收纳那些不为人知的“<strong>收容物</strong>”，他们是失落的神迹与禁忌的力量。同时街头巷尾的隐秘角落里，还流传着获得超凡之力的方法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184990/extras/a5d3d5f44eb19f25fbf733fcaa51d282.poster.avif?t=1768359020\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184990/extras/a5d3d5f44eb19f25fbf733fcaa51d282.webm?t=1768359020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184990/extras/a5d3d5f44eb19f25fbf733fcaa51d282.mp4?t=1768359020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>实装了AI玩法的全新推理体验</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以拿任何证物向任何人询问。也许你严谨的推理会使嫌疑人恐惧破防，又或者你会收获意料之外的答案。有别于其他推理游戏，《诡秘推理》有大量的实时对话，每一个NPC都不止是一个普通角色，而是你与思维共舞的推理对手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>四十万字级别的剧情</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >约40万字的诡谲狂想，环环相扣的案件逻辑，丰富多样的出场人物。共计4个核心案件，并提供多种可能性的结局（3个主线结局+20个支线结局）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184990/extras/f53675c54e0652ec8c6f6d9efa04ffcc.poster.avif?t=1768359020\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184990/extras/f53675c54e0652ec8c6f6d9efa04ffcc.webm?t=1768359020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184990/extras/f53675c54e0652ec8c6f6d9efa04ffcc.mp4?t=1768359020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多种攻略途径抓获真凶</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强制的 “搜证阶段+推理阶段” 的玩法有时玩起来是有点挫败的，特别是卡在“还差一个证物在哪里？&quot;的时候。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《诡秘推理》打破经典推理玩法中的线性演出流程，鼓励玩家按自己的节奏在地图中自由行走，搜查现场、串联线索；案件谜题也能通过不同推理路线层层破解，有多种解法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184990/extras/ceb4b546c94011ecb2dddf7ab837945c.poster.avif?t=1768359020\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184990/extras/ceb4b546c94011ecb2dddf7ab837945c.webm?t=1768359020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184990/extras/ceb4b546c94011ecb2dddf7ab837945c.mp4?t=1768359020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">调查现场</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184990/extras/744cc428b9df1d68ed727231d08b6af9.poster.avif?t=1768359020\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184990/extras/744cc428b9df1d68ed727231d08b6af9.webm?t=1768359020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184990/extras/744cc428b9df1d68ed727231d08b6af9.mp4?t=1768359020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">出示证物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184990/extras/15a32357e5c5ae75c094534f4e61fe8b.poster.avif?t=1768359020\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184990/extras/15a32357e5c5ae75c094534f4e61fe8b.webm?t=1768359020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184990/extras/15a32357e5c5ae75c094534f4e61fe8b.mp4?t=1768359020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">与嫌疑人自由对话（套话！审讯！或者再聊点什么别的？）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>创新玩法 “深度推理” 实时对话中暗藏玄机</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们设计了“深度推理”，进一步提高了游戏的可玩性，以及可探索的深度。充分发挥了自由对话这一玩法的乐趣，喜欢探索的玩家可以与NPC们畅所欲言，每一段对话都可能暗藏线索，每一次互动都可能揭开未知的谜题——世界不止于表面，真相等待被你挖掘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184990/extras/b8f9965feb481d9c94cc827d08f271b9.poster.avif?t=1768359020\" width=966 height=544 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184990/extras/b8f9965feb481d9c94cc827d08f271b9.webm?t=1768359020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184990/extras/b8f9965feb481d9c94cc827d08f271b9.mp4?t=1768359020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>快速通关秘诀是...“角色扮演”?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是的，就是“<strong>角色扮演</strong>”。虽然你的职业是“侦探”，但有时为了真相也不得不“扮演”其他的&quot;职业&quot;。为了让你的扮演起来更加有趣（不只是NPC）。“扮演法”具体怎么玩？一点点剧透如下：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤓🤡，🤐🤔🥴😃🤫🧐</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>角色介绍</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184990/extras/c787f6bccae5ba868fde20ee7bb3a529.avif?t=1768359020\" width=1600 height=900 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >姓名：月见抒</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年龄：？？？（不要问，没有活人知道）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >种族：？？？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >职业：AIB行动处处长</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高冷神秘的气质、极少流露私人情绪，擅长制定计划并严格执行。七神的秩序才是唯一准则。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184990/extras/cc34a97554bbadc548e881e146773bf0.avif?t=1768359020\" width=1600 height=900 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >姓名：莫鱼</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年龄：25</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >职业：新晋探员</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从学校毕业，进入稽查局工作，成为新起之秀，当然也会时不时地摸摸鱼。在调查马丁公馆命案时被卷入超凡事件，但他也在寻找着重新回归普通人生活的方法。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><br>当然还有更多神秘的登场角色....</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184990/extras/27b0f00cb4cecc8284a81e5c1bfe9238.avif?t=1768359020\" width=1600 height=900 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>那么，你准备好迎接未知了吗？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《诡秘推理》</strong> 将带你进入一个不可预测的精神迷宫，挑战你的思维极限，看看你能否在这个混乱的世界中找出真相！还是会逐渐陷入疯狂...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
